cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CY 

The paper proposes a natural language understanding task of discovering diverse perspectives about claims, which involves text data processing and analysis. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-categories of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Machine Learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper involves information retrieval (cs.IR) and cybersecurity (cs.CY) aspects, as it deals with the contamination of information supply and the need to filter out noise in the dataset.
